(299,581,'【WATASHIBA】Lesson Reservation Completed','Dear #STUDENT_NAME#.\n\nThank you for taking the WATASHIBA.\nWe have received your reservation for the following lesson.\nThe details of your reservation are as follows. Please check it once again.\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\nLesson date: #LESSON_DATE#\nLesson start time: #LESSON_TIME#\nLesson name: #LESSON_NAME#\r\nCourse name: #COURSE_NAME#\nLesson text name: #LESSON_TEXT_NAME#\nLecturer nickname: #TEACHER_NICKNAME#\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nWhen it is 5 minutes before the lesson starts, please login to the My Page and click the Start Lesson button to start the lesson.\n My page login link: \r\n#ZOOM_URL#\n\nThe lesson will be conducted via zoom, so if you do not have the zoom app installed, please install it on your device in advance.\n zoom usage guide link, etc. \n\nYou can check and change your registration information from \"\"Basic Information\"\" in \"\"Change Registration Information\"\" on My Page.\n#TEACHER_PROFILE_URL#\r\n\nIf you do not hear from your tutor when the lesson time comes, please contact the Customer Service Center.\n\nWe look forward to seeing #STUDENT_NAME# at the lesson.\n\nPlease do not reply to this email as this is a send-only address. \nWe are unable to respond to your inquiry even if you reply to this email.\n\n.....................................................................................................................\nContact information\n\n.....................................................................................................................','en'),
